Text:
Starts off genuinely unimpressive. Sure she has a really nice body, but she's missing a tooth or two and during introduction and "forplay" she seems really bored and just not into it, like it's really just another job. Which it is, of course, but I mean it shouldn't look it.
But as soon as they get to the actual fucking she flicks some kinda switch and seems to REALLY get into it, and it turns out one of the better doggy-scenes I've seen. At least if you're into BALL chicks, like me.
